data.description: A Rare Single-Story Gem in North West Ridgecrest. This hard-to-find well-maintained home is located in The Estates. A gorgeous drive up gives way to a low maintenance rockscaped front yard and an oversized lot that features RV parking with double gates. Step into this split floorplan that features 2 separate primary bedrooms on opposite sides of the home, and 2 additional sizable bedrooms, and a 3rd full guest bathroom. Enjoy entertaining guests with your private dining room or delight your guests in your kitchen space that features a large breakfast bar area overlooking your family room. Meticulous attention to details is presented in this kitchen with granite counters tops and decorative custom backsplash with under cabinet lighting. Tile Flooring is featured through most of the home, which will help keep the temperature down on those hot summer days. The oversized main primary bedroom features ample natural light, and step into your ensuite where you can escape for your very own spa retreat. This bedroom also features private access to your backyard. If you love outdoor living space, you'll love hosting your summertime BBQ's in this spacious backyard with your covered patio, or practice your swing, or putt in this drought resistant backyard. You'll also appreciate the 2 oversized large sheds, which one of them is insulated to store extra stuff. The one thing about the desert is the summer evenings, & You'll never miss your desert sunsets in this backyard. Don't sweat high energy bills because this beauty has paid off solar. Any buyer who's looking for a 3 car garage on a premium sized lot will know that this may not last, and we hope this inspires you to act fast.
